br />\n<br />\n優厚薪酬待遇<br />\n銀行假期<br />\n年假從14至22天開始（根據年資，職級）<br />\n娛樂津貼每年高達HKD1,000<br />\n醫療和牙科保險 <br />\n<br />\n個老細刻薄員工，請私家廚就肯洗錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc6ea51b964d084a1060afe67695c40819e2ea","tid":1818468,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"樓主肯開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面有冇彩虹小馬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df8abe03dc0fe0e6d8e7d76490bc2eb92a21f78","tid":1818468,"uid":73991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"仲以為講緊asl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2431993a04fd0f2874fc7bcae2708a92182b86b","tid":1818468,"uid":256143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df8abe03dc0fe0e6d8e7d76490bc2eb92a21f78","tid":1818468,"uid":73991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"仲以為講緊asl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"2b570a3882fc5fdd0b04651bd34373a2a1f1a7ff","tid":1818468,"uid":163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ff142b808fa46a2649faafc381ed14a1434cdd","tid":1818468,"uid":59902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"屌那星 jobsdb長期見佢地d post<br />\nthanks 樓主share"},{"pid":"861c57903294d767bc1780317806e2d13487ef45","tid":1818468,"uid":167435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"睇個名都知似係厄 funding 啲等執嘅垃圾 vendor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c655fc2f0450c3ede6809d4b9cb1937c2fc3ed1"